TM TT LUN VN THC S
ti: Xy dng chatbot h tr quyt nh, t vn mua hng trong ng dng chat.
Tc gi lun vn: Trn ng Tuyn Kha: 2019B
Ngi hng dn: TS. Phm Huy Hong
T kha (Keyword): Chatbot, RASA, RNN, LSTM, Neural network, k thut hc my,
training model, intents, responses, transformer, DIETClassifier, pepiline, component,
x l ngn ng t nhin (NLP),
Ni dung tm tt:
a) L do chn ti
-
S lc v lch s chatbot v phn loi.
-
Vi s ph bin ca chatbot v nhng nn tng xy dng chatbot hin
nay, nhm mc ch phn loi, la chn mt gii php tip cn, tc gi
la chn nghin cu v s dng RASA Framework.
b) Mc ch nghin cu ca lun vn, i tng, phm vi nghin cu.
-
Nghin cu cc bc xy dng mt chatbot trong min ng, quy trnh
chnh gm c:
Xc nh nh ngi dng
Trch xut thng tin
Qun l hi thoi
M hnh sinh hi thoi cho chatbot
-
Phn tch RASA framework, v s dng m ngun m nn s tp trung
vo nhng cu hnh chnh ca loi chatbot t vn mua hng.
-
S dng b d liu hi thoi ca doanh nghip c th l Petrolimex. Vi
1548 mu, c tin x l v phn loi s dng hun luyn chatbot.
c) Tm tt c ng cc thnh phn chnh
-
Chng 1: Trnh by tnh cn thit ca chatbot, phn tch la chn cng
c nn tng ph hp tip tc nghin cu. a ra so snh nh gi cc
nn tng hin ti. La chn hng nghin cu c th l RASA.
-
Chng 2: Nghin cu, phn tch tp trung v RASA framework. Cc k
thut s dng, thnh phn, cu hnh.
-
Chng 3: p dng vo bi ton thc t ti doanh nghip. Xy dng b
d liu, tin x l v chun ha. Xy dng chng trnh. nh gi kt
qu trin khai m hnh. Kt ni ng dng.
d) Kt qu th nghim v nh gi
-
nh gi m hnh hot ng vi chnh xc cao, khong 75%. C kh
nng trin khai trn h thng thc t ti doanh nghip.
-
ng dng kt ni thnh cng qua API.
-
a ra nhng hn ch, nh hng pht trin tip theo.
e) Kt lun
ti nghin cu cc kin thc v chatbot bao gm lch s, kin trc, nhim v,
cc thnh phn cu thnh, cc thut ton c bn p dng. gii quyt bi ton theo
hng tip cn min ng, c th l lnh vc t vn h tr khch hng s dng dch v.
Trn c s c th tip tc pht trin ng dng cho cc lnh vc khc trong thc t
qua chatbot.
